Package com.bt.npm.netrep.common

Interface Summary
IComparator The comparator interface to be implemented by the Different comparators DB basedcomparison, File based comparison
IWriter This is the base interface for supporting any writing logic.
 

Class Summary
DeltaCreater Common implementation for DB and File based delta creation logic
FileBasedDeltaCreater It is used to compare the records in two different files and gives the delta out of it.
IndexTable<K,V> Own HashMap extension to avoid the null keys and control the duplicates
and have control on serial key
InventoryResourceLoader This class is to load the inventory files related information.
NpmFileParser The class is designed to read flat files (text-based) where each line of the file is considered to be a record.
NpmFileWriter This class is designed to write into a given file Object/Path.
